{
  "stem": "4670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember my dad discussing the fact that it had this crack on, which was, he said, it's caused by the glazes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we know they were valuable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He also had a little ivory paintbrush holder, which he got from that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's the only thing that I have that came out of there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have it here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I'll show it to you later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the vases and also a samovar, which is a sort of a brass pot with these lions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They're very valuable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And a painting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, those were visible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Those three things were visible-- or four things-- two vase and that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And apparently, someone must have told someone, some of the Nazis that we had this valuable artwork.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because they came to us in our apartment, and they said, you're donating that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We are going to take that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Actually, what they did is they just took it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we said, yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We never saw it again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "These-- these were really our valuables.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the time came that my dad had to leave Germany and we knew we'd have to leave, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And at the time, I don't remember, you know, it was stressful, and I don't remember exactly what we did with the store.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He somehow dissolved it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I'm sure he didn't sell it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But he did slowly, after April of 1933, began to take some money out of the bank.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He had some accounts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Not everything, but he took as much as he could slowly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He then had a friend in a nearby town, which was called Offenbach, which was also involved in the leather good business.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And there was a-- one of our friends who was Jewish, who was a repairman, and he took a briefcase.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
